text:
Bella Hadid and Kendall Jenner Hit the Strip Club in Paris Because what happens in Paris stays in…wait, no. That’s not right. 
BY KAYLEIGH ROBERTS MAR 2, 2017 Walking the runway is tough work, and after a long shift at the H&M show in Paris, Bella Hadid, Kendall Jenner, Hailey Baldwin, Jasmine Sanders, and Lily Donaldson needed to unwind. So they went to a Paris strip club, naturally. A post shared by Bella Hadid (@bellahadid) on Mar 1, 2017 at 3:30pm PST A post shared by Kendall (@kendalljenner) on Mar 1, 2017 at 3:10pm PST 
According to E! Online , the models were spotted at the Pink Paradise strip club, before heading over to the Lark nightclub. A post shared by Hailey Baldwin News (@hlybaldwin) on Mar 2, 2017 at 10:29am PST A post shared by Pink Paradise Official (@pinkparadiseparis) on Mar 2, 2017 at 8:03am PST The girls’ night out couldn’t have come at a better time —as Bella’s ex The Weeknd and his new girlfriend Selena Gomez were staying at a hotel just a few blocks away from Bella’s earlier this week. Awkward. This post originally appeared on elle.com
